text: Golam Rahman Shah is a Bangladesh Awami League politician and the former Member of Parliament of Dinajpur-6. ==Career== Shah was elected to parliament from Dinajpur-6 as a Bangladesh Awami League candidate in 1979. ==References== Category:Awami League politicians Category:Living people Category:2nd Jatiya Sangsad members Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
title: Golam Rahman Shah
